Description: MythicOS bootable USB creator (CLI + GUI)
 Rufus-like MythicOS USB creator for Linux with both command-line
 and graphical interfaces.
 .
 Features include:
  - listing removable USB devices,
  - ISO verification,
  - writing a bootable image to USB with safety checks.
